name: Suzaku - The Guardian of The South
description:
Suzaku is the guardian of the south. Suzaku is one of The Four Protectors whose protect the metaverse from four major directions.
He is associated with the element of fire and the color red. He represents the virtue of propriety. He controls heat and flame.
Suzaku represents a symbol of loyalty, kindness, zeal, and nobility.

Suzaku is the Second guardian in the series of 'The Four Protectors' by hudxhoods
